Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候确实是杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事实不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是我在这里陈述这一切的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的认罪状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿之后的两周  谁都不记得他在班级里存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有和他有着密切关系的我还记着他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得这只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我趁着记忆还清晰的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里记录如何才能停止灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  让死者回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让死者回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是停止已经开始的灾难的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上小学的时候  有一个和她很像的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她指的是见崎同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎同学明明是独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也没和我同班过  大家都叫她「Misaki」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从见崎家的地址来看  应该不可能和你一个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  所以我才说奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左眼的眼罩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没戴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她四岁就失去了左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙参加这次的合宿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「另一个人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像杀了人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原  发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你们俩一个问题  听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识风见智彦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在问你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见智彦这个人认识吗  是个什么样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然认识了  既是班长又是你的孽缘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎弄错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄错？弄错什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我彻底把他当成「另一个人」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…  该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下杀手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这种谎话有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试探了他一下  因为他最近感觉很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  他竟然忘记了我们俩小时候一起干过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学时候的事情也不太记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心去追问了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你其实不是风见吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你才是混入班级的另一个人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着他一下子就变得很紧张  慌了神  最后还对我发了火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑  果然是这家伙没错  当时我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个磁带所说的一样  他死掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者回归死亡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就都能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你…杀了他？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是真的想杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个扭打在一起  到了外面的阳台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经倒在地上不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血从头上流了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我变得害怕起来  跑到了走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看到榊进了这间房间所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认了吗  风见同学是不是「另一个人」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「另一个人」死掉的话  他马上就会变成不存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们却记得风见…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是我弄错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  榊  到底怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄错了  或者是还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两楼的高度不一定会摔死人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里看不到树丛的对面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在先确认风见同学是不是还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前岛同学  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你被人捅了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去偷看了一眼食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前岛同学  快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵什么呢  恒一同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊  发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在那儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前岛同学  他受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人捅了一刀  而且食堂着大火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员在里面死了  被人杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那个犯人放的火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…多佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把前岛同学抬到安全的地方  打119
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和多佳子的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  多佳子被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子  你在哪儿  多佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有见到杉浦同学和风见同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到过风见同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才他浑身是泥面无血色地来了我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说  敕使河原变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然气势汹汹地  问我发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我把磁带的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了  录音机不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊  风见呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前岛同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他交给听到惨叫跑出来的同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分头找风见同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有去每个房间让大家逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着火了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且食堂已经是一片火海了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见也不知所踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱成一团了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点告诉三神老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  三神老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道三神老师出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  现在先出去报警比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  得先确认三神老师是否安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和望月同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从下面传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  泉美也死了的话我也活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉美没有我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者回归死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原同学  快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说让死者回归死亡…  为什么杉浦同学会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她听了磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前的三班找到的吧  小椋告诉她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来寻找停止灾难的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  在这里听了磁带？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  从望月同学那儿拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为对策组成员一定得去听听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么说见崎是死者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子从海边回来以后  精神上受了很大打击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把多佳子找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤泽同学  一个人太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策组给三班同学的重要通知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要播放的磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是十五年前  灾难中途停止的那年遗留下来的磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉大家如何才能停止灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  让死者回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让死者回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是停止已经开始的灾难的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  十五年前的灾难被中途阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且  今年的死者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以这么说  是因为我在小学时和没有失去左眼的见崎同学同校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在她却失去了左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不完全地复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的见崎鸣是假冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让死者回归死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归死亡吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让死者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三神老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以杀害自己的同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要让死者回归死亡  就不会再出现牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要杀了见崎就能阻止灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！这绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那死者到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个死者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我哥哥偿命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意很滑  小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让死者回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小椋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在走廊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从下面包抄他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得真的是见崎同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女的感觉很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是…不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有闻到什么焦臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像说是火灾来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没看见火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是食堂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是食堂发生了爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒在食堂门口的前岛同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是让杉浦同学给…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是那个老太婆干的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很碍事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你并不是死者  所以我不会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且泉美还蛮喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让死者…回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤泽同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎…鸣！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  赤泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦同学她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我不宰了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果死者消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会发生这么悲伤的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎！


